06fe5a520c7953f9ca19a18c13","tid":1860041,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"林鄭條閪婆真心痴撚左線"},{"pid":"e14112527d9e3f5d72691e174d9215d49d029de1","tid":1860041,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa8a4f9005c9c00d0f35250c0d4725df89e0edb3","tid":1860041,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b597068f52bc32fa2a5a66692517872c1fb4230","tid":1860041,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cc146eca095e451c7b116a562832a72658e8859","tid":1860041,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31548f03042408d982ef9af4dbabaac565a4c2b7","tid":1860041,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"放工聽完柒頭個十九記招，大約總結如下:<br />\n1. 關我就唔會封<br />\n2. 醫護罷工有成效，但港共唔封關既目的並唔係主要關醫護事<br />\n3. 口罩同防護裝備我就唔會派街坊，你班港燦自己諗掂去<br />\n<br />\n而港共點解會有以上三點?<br />\n<br />\n1. 封關戰線<br />\n點解企咁硬唔封關？<br />\n好多人都話林鄭同你班唔聽話既香港人鬥氣。<br />\n我認為呢一點係有，但係佔既比例極細。<br />\n香港作為中國連接國際既港口，<br />\n唔到你一個林鄭話封就封，<br />\n上面又H5N1 又武肺 又鼠疫 又豬瘟 又地震 又民變<br />\n咁多樣野齊晒，班所謂既共官，其實都要逃生門走難<br />\n而香港就係個班官同權貴既最後逃生門<br />\n一日班官同有錢佬未走晒，香港個關都唔會封<br />\n<br />\n學天琦講: 認為勇武抗爭有用既，就做；認為靜坐、罷工、罷交稅有用，一樣照做<br />\n我地唔要教條主義，抗爭必須多元化，係唔同抗爭手段上互補長短。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>第一，封關 - 醫護罷工戰線</strong></span></span><br />\n林鄭條八婆擺到明係拖到有病人死，然後大做文章攻擊你地。<br />\n但希望醫護手足可以堅持，未必係一兩個星期內會見到成果。<br />\n其他行業亦要將自己疫情慘況無限放大，吹風叫身邊既人嘗試唔返工、射波<br />\n多人去反思點解返工要搵命搏，咁樣各行各業都可以促成今次罷工，<br />\n咁樣醫護手足先唔會被炮火針對攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">同樣係封關 - 勇武戰線</span></strong></span><br />\n首先，小弟在此對各2014年以來各位勇武手足及近日自行封關手足，致最高敬意。<br />\n點解港共只封淨三個關口，其實各位勇武手足應該心中有數。<br />\n留返三個難以全身而退既關口，設既係陷阱去活捉炸彈人。<br />\n因為呢班手足先係最有行動力，用最少人數，但卻可以做出最大效果既一群<br />\n港共必定會針對你地，千方百計要活捉你地。<br />\n係連登呢D公海，只可以同你地講萬事小心，無論你地搞唔搞落去，<br />\n小弟都支持同尊重理解你地既決定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">另外，封關 - 國際戰線</span></span></strong><br />\n上面講過林鄭係唔會自己封左逃生門，所以佢最驚係外國主動封香港<br />\n而近日林鄭條八婆既假封關，其實有呃到人，佢唔係要外國完全唔封，<br />\n拖得一秒，佢贏得一秒。<br />\n所謂要將林鄭假封關既資料同數據瘋狂轉發上Twitter，要真係做到洗版式。<br />\n將香港係國際網絡平台上，直接講述返香港現時既實際狀況。<br />\n<br />\n如果外國封香港 如果全港大罷工成功<br />\n其實唔需要有炸彈人出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">另一個戰場 - 搶口罩潮</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實港共操作好明顯，林鄭做醜人，建制派做好人<br />\n小弟懷疑政府既口罩除左運上中國媚共外，<br />\n其實仲扣起左預留比建制派派街坊，用口罩換返選票，<br />\n一方面安撫建制派，另一方面令到班港豬中立撚覺得自己受過建制派恩賜。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搶口罩潮 - 黃色經濟圈</span></span></strong><br />\n政府唔做，自己做。<br />\n建議各位黃店可以用網店方式去賣口罩，以減少廢老藍絲落鋪面搞事<br />\n某黃店亦打算自行生產，可以參考，重整返香港本土既工業。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搶口罩潮 - 工會</span></span></strong><br />\n希望早前手足組成既工會，可以用經費購入防疫用口分發比成員，<br />\n一來可以吸納更多成員，為下次罷工做好準備，<br />\n二來令更多人明白黃圈先係真心為社會，<br />\n吸納更多黃人，為群眾可以更理解罷工或勇武各種抗爭手段。<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">自己香港，自己救。<br />\n天祐義人</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"大家除咗罷工之外，唔好唔記得<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國戰線</span></span></strong>，向美國遊說請求美國就封關事宜以及85000僑民嘅性命安全向港共施壓，同埋邀請CDC派員嚟香港協助抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fexert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=c8e91b89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=051fdea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter：<br />\nNCM Yue<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=629f2f04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue</a><br />\n美國國務院<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StateDept\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStateDept&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=662903e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StateDept</a><br />\n美國駐港總領事館<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAinHKMacau&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=62ba9e1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau</a><br />\n<br />\nFb：<br />\n美國駐港總領事館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USAinHKMacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSAinHKMacau&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=7e7dc3c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/USAinHKMacau</a>"},{"pid":"0802ce475064f42036f269a25c306325fca8dd69","tid":1860041,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"政府堅持 冇事<br />\n民間堅持 嚴重。<br />\n醫療專家堅持 嚴重<br />\n<br />\n有冇似番d 樣既第三方醫療組織評論下香港？"}]}